<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/42129163-fearing-the-black-body"><img alt="Fearing the Black Body: The Racial Origins of Fat Phobia" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1547064637l/42129163._SX98_.jpg" />
